descriptionNullable:
# Description
Historical hourly prices for stocks (7000+) traded on NASDAQ from 2021-01-01 to 2021-12-30. 

# Data
See [provenance](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/leukipp/hourly-stock-prices/metadata), times based on stock exchange location:
- `ticker` (*string*): Symbol name.
- `name` (*string*): Security name.
- `date` (*string*): Trading date (Eastern Time Zone).
- `open` (*float*): Open price on that day.
- `high` (*float*): Maximum price on that day.
- `low` (*float*): Minimum price on that day.
- `close` (*float*): Close price on that day.
- `adjusted close` (*float*): Close price adjusted for dividends and splits.
- `volume` (*int*): Share volume traded on that day.

# Usage
See [getting started](https://www.kaggle.com/code/leukipp/hourly-stock-prices-getting-started), data available as *csv*.
